This directory contains the source for the CLX Programmer's Reference Manual
(roughly 230 pages). Look in ../../hardcopy/CLX for the files in PostScript
format.

For convenience, the sections can be printed separately as follows:

 contents.doc      ; Cover, table of contents
 s01.doc           ; Introduction to CLX
 s02.doc           ; Displays 
 s03.doc           ; Screens
 s04.doc           ; Windows and pixmaps
 s05.doc           ; Graphics contexts
 s06.doc           ; Graphic operations
 s07.doc           ; Images
 s08.doc           ; Fonts and characters
 s09.doc           ; Colors
 s10.doc           ; Cursors
 s11.doc           ; Atoms, properties, and selections
 s12.doc           ; Events and input
 s13.doc           ; Resources
 s14.doc           ; Control functions
 s15.doc           ; Extensions
 s16.doc           ; Errors
 appa.doc          ; Protocol vs CLX function cross-ref
 glossary.doc      ; Glossary
 general.doc       ; Index - general
 condition.doc     ;         conditions
 functions.doc     ;         functions
 types.doc         ;         types
